Interested in joining Buckeye Twirl? Tryouts for our club and competition team are on Monday August 21st @ the RPAC room A200! Open gym is available for anyone wanting to warm up or stretch. Tryouts will begin promptly at 5:00pm. Please look at the flyers attached for important information regarding tricks, attire, and our teams.  New to baton twirling? Join our Beginner Skills team and learn how to twirl from our BT members. No tryouts are needed for Beginner Skills team. Pl...ease email us if interested. If you have any questions regarding tryouts or Beginner Skills team, please email us at ohiostatebuckeyetwirl@gmail.com or follow our team page on Facebook and Instagram @Buckeye Twirl Hope to see you there!
